    "body": "I think a pattern is going to be too abstract, but what we could potentially do is grab 1200 images from https://www.pexels.com/popular-photos/all-time/ remove any NSFW images and then \r\nscale&crop them down to a dimension (ie `300x50`) at 60% jpg quality each image would be 2-3kb and adding only 3MB to filesize. Could potentially reduce phishing ability down to 1 in 1000 and still look aesthetically pleasing and recognisable.  ",
